LOCAL 0 = No. of samples in the buffer
LOCAL 1 = Sequence No. of the packet
BUFFER 0 = Packet to be sent out
typedef struct _pkt_format {
 uint16_t seq_no;
 uint16_t samples[]; // No. of samples is push value in line 19
} pkt_format_t;

Packet is broadcast to 
Message Type: Push value in line 30
Module Id: Push value in line 32


Timer Restart period is push value in line 38.
This value should be the same as the value set in 
reboot timer script.